OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, UK retail sales fell by 1.4% in March  
OL,6, as the rising cost of living hit       
OL,7, consumer spending, according to        
OL,8, official data.                         
OL,10,FOnline sales were hit particularly hard
OL,11,Fas people tightened their belts, the   
OL,12,FOffice for National Statistics said.   
OL,14,FFuel sales also fell as people cut     
OL,15,Fnon-essential travel amid record petrol
OL,16,Fand diesel prices.                     
OL,18,FHowever, overall retail sales were     
OL,19,Fstill 2.2% above pre-Covid levels, the 
OL,20,FONS said.                              
